{"type": "article", "id": 9605, "title": "Denis Dolganov 扬声器", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-15T07:10:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235544VgOYbWQAv0tDNZs1.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t乌克兰设计师 Denis Dolganov 设计的这一款蓝牙扬声器看起来像极了我们小时候玩儿的听筒游戏：两个杯子用一根线连在一起，两个小伙伴一个说一个听，便可以隔着空气说悄悄话了。他的灵感来源的确是这种小玩具。两个扬声器之间用一根可以伸缩的线连接，使用者可以把他们系在任何他们希望看到的位置。这是<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/pten\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的个人主页</a>，点击可以查看更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052355426TluzCBrK72sdLhU.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235542Blznq4XbgYftQec9.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235542lHvejtSm1NUPk45c.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052355431DSuxHYgJE5pRftZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.67962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052355431eEhWj9NScD3LHJX.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.33888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}